Arta performed in-country, regionally and internationally in well-known theatre festivals in Europe and elsewhere. She started her career with plays in National Theatre in Tirana, Albania such as:



Gënjeshtari (Liar) ,K.Goldon,  Directed by: Ervin Çuli, Part: Rosaura;


Vdekja e Dantonit (Danton’s death) ,G.Byhner, Directed by: Vladimir Milcin, Part: Lysi; “Quo Vadis” 


S.Fanko, Directed by: Serafin Fanko, Part: Bride;


Ditë vere (Summer Day), S.Mrozhek, Directed by: Bojken Lako, Part: Dama (Lady) and 


Kujdes kafshon (Watch out it bites) , A. Bern, Directed by: Kico Londo, Part: Kate.
